VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)execute\s(\@|\()
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:(Request\.|QueryString|Form|userInput|args) && MISSING:(allowlist|whitelist|argument escaping|ProcessStartInfo)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of command execution methods that can introduce security vulnerabilities.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Unsafe Method: Command Execution.
